<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">⚠️ Payment Issue with Your Subscription</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @customer.full_name %>,</p>

<div style="background: #fee2e2; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #991b1b; font-weight: 600;">
    Payment Failed
  </p>
  <p style="margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px;">
    We were unable to process your payment for your <%= @plan.name %> subscription.
  </p>
</div>

<p>
  <% if @failed_count == 1 %>
    This is the first time we've had trouble processing your payment. Don't worry - we'll try again automatically.
  <% elsif @failed_count == 2 %>
    We've now attempted to charge your payment method twice without success. We'll make one more automatic attempt.
  <% elsif @failed_count >= 3 %>
    We've made <%= @failed_count %> attempts to charge your payment method without success. Your subscription may be suspended soon.
  <% end %>
</p>

<div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937;">What you can do:</p>
  <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #6b7280;">
    <li>Check that your payment method has sufficient funds</li>
    <li>Verify that your card hasn't expired</li>
    <li>Update your payment method if needed</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
  <%= link_to "Update Payment Method", @update_payment_url, style: "display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #8B4513; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;" %>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reply to this email.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">
  Best regards,<br>
  <strong>The Acer Coffee Team</strong>
</p>
